<note n="0065006" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0065006">實＝說【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0067001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0067001">故＝者【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0067002" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0067002">知無為＝無為名【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
</p>
