<cb:div type="taisho-notes">
<head>大正 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0062006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062006">三藏＝沙門統大乘論師【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0062007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062007">流＝留【元】【明】＊</note>
<note n="0062008" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062008">（第三）＋譯【元】＊</note>
<note n="0062009" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062009">〔歸命…薩〕八字－【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0062010" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062010">坐＝座【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0062011" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0062011">思惟＝惟念【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063001">忘＝妄【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063002">垢＝姤【宋】，始【元】【明】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063003">菩薩＝眾生【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063004">惟＝唯【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0063005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063005">輪＝轉【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063006">諮＝請【宋】【宮】</note>
<note n="0063007" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0063007">（不見…故）九字＝於他闕失不見其過故【元】依明校異，南藏亦然</note>
<note n="0064001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064001">佛名智無減＝佛智無減少【宮】</note>
<note n="0064002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064002">天四＝四天【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0064003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064003">惓＝倦【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0064004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0064004">往＝住【三】【宮】＊</note>
<note n="0065001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065001">者＝著【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0065002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065002">憶＝億【明】</note>
<note n="0065003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065003">歎＝歡【元】</note>
<note n="0065004" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065004">心＋（念）【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0065005" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065005">達解＝解達【宮】</note>
<note n="0065006" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0065006">實＝說【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0066001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066001">諸＝說【宮】</note>
<note n="0066002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066002">辦＝辯【宮】</note>
<note n="0066003" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0066003">問＝謂【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0067001" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067001">故＝者【三】【宮】</note>
<note n="0067002" resp="#resp1" type="orig" place="foot text" target="#nkr_note_orig_0067002">知無為＝無為名【三】【宮】</note>
</p>
